'''Makgaung''' ke toropo go feta [[Maruleng Mmusogae]], [[Mmasepala Setereke tša Mopani]] wa diporofense [[Limpopo]] kamoka [[Afrika Borwa]].

Makgaung has three primary schools: Makgaung primary school, Mamokaile primary school and Hope combine school. Two secondary schools are located in Makgaung. 

